summary: A motivated woman with over 10 years of experienced in working with people, experienced lawyer. Professional, who gained experience through leading projects and lecturing at university, whose successes can be seen in multiple roles. Since 2017 a Member of Polish Professional Women in the Netherlands, responsible for helping polish people with the new reality.
